<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ваш профиль</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('/background.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-in-out;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            margin-top: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .user-info {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .user-info p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {{> header}}
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Добро пожаловать в ваш профиль, {{user}}</h1>
        <div class="user-info">
            <p><strong>Имя пользователя:</strong> {{user}}</p>
            <p><strong>Электронная почта:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        </div>
        
        {{> profileHeader}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
